    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/457680/extras/fd2ab95eff5b9bdfd2598f0212ad7fc1.avif?t=1709177024\" width=616 height=120 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/457680/extras/1a7282cc8ddfb4e8953942e366c9d514.poster.avif?t=1709177024\" width=600 height=364 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/457680/extras/1a7282cc8ddfb4e8953942e366c9d514.webm?t=1709177024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/457680/extras/1a7282cc8ddfb4e8953942e366c9d514.mp4?t=1709177024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>OPUS：地球计划，获得众多国际大奖肯定的叙事冒险游戏终于登陆 Steam 了！主打知名的感情丰富的暖心故事，由 IMGA 大奖提名编剧执笔。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >地球真的存在吗？</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/457680/extras/f45b9a090786e174962c432a0ebcc490.webp?t=1709177024\" width=604 height=4 /></span><br><br>银河历 160000 年，人类经历好几世纪的太空移民，忘了地球的位置，地球已成为人类神话中的故乡。长期进行基因改造的人类，陷入灭亡危机，唯有找到地球、找到人类原始的 DNA，才有机会修复基因缺陷。一艘太空船承载了全人类的希望，展开史称“地球探索计划”的星际旅行。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/457680/extras/9823eb105a825b0ad2947d380877b562.avif?t=1709177024\" width=616 height=66 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/457680/extras/76ce0ad9f4863df58dc4b4f83f47ac77.avif?t=1709177024\" width=616 height=200 /></span><br><br><i>“没有目标的机器人就只是台计算机。所以听好啰...你的目标，就是找到地球。跟博士约好了喔？”</i><br>- 丽莎博士<br> <br><i>“艾姆会找到地球！艾姆跟博士约好了。”</i><br>- 艾姆<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/457680/extras/8d9022871cc4cead097296f0718be62d.avif?t=1709177024\" width=616 height=200 /></span><br><br>OPUS：地球计划是一款剧情丰富的解谜探索游戏。你将帮助机器人艾姆，完成一段跨越数个世纪的约定，同时探索生命的初衷，以及自己诞生的理由。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/457680/extras/f45b9a090786e174962c432a0ebcc490.webp?t=1709177024\" width=604 height=4 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>像个 NASA 科学家操作一部可以不断装备、进化的太空望远近，借由扫描不断发现新的行星</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>在丰富多变的太空漫游，沉浸在我们手工打造的宇宙景致</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>探索充满谜团的太空船，调查太空船中的物件，揭开古老任务的历史</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>揭开太空船成员们的过去，和他们旅行的目的</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>在一片星海中，找到传说中的古老行星——地球</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>超过 20 首会随着宇宙地景改变，由独立游戏大奖提名乐师 Triodust 为游戏量身打造的音乐</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>电影般的科幻冒险故事，将带给你回味无穷的感动</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/457680/extras/fb37e74f0068901aecc5abc2aba9a0bd.poster.avif?t=1709177024\" width=600 height=364 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/457680/extras/fb37e74f0068901aecc5abc2aba9a0bd.webm?t=1709177024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/457680/extras/fb37e74f0068901aecc5abc2aba9a0bd.mp4?t=1709177024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/457680/extras/396cfd082a859b783c530e58fd8af045.webp?t=1709177024\" width=604 height=3 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/457680/extras/747cd935819d311d863a12270f2f659a.avif?t=1709177024\" width=616 height=66 /></span>",
